title: ML-DS1, LSD1 inhibitor, rep1
characteristics_ch1: tissue: patient sample expanded via xenotransplantation
treatment_protocol_ch1: ML-DS patient samples were treated with DMSO (vehicle control), 350nM of the LSD1 inhibitor T-3775440, 1uM ruxolitinib, or the combination of T-3775440 and ruxolitinib for 48 hours.
growth_protocol_ch1: Patient samples were maintained in StemSpan supplemental with a cytokine cocktail (FLT3-L, SCF, IL-6, IL-3, TPO) for the duration of the treatment (48 hours).
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted using the Zymo Quick-RNA Miniprep Kit with on-column DNase treatment (R1054).
extract_protocol_ch1.1: Illumina sequencing libraries were prepared by Novogene Company, Ltd. using total cellular RNA, and sequenced on an Illumina NovaSeq platform (150 bp paired-end reads).
data_processing: Raw reads were trimmed and filtered by Novogene Company, Ltd. using in-house scripts, then mapped to human reference genome hg38 using HISAT2.
data_processing.1: Gene expression values (FPKM) were calculated using the featureCounts package in R.
data_processing.3: Supplementary files format and content: Normalized read counts (FPKM) in tab-separated format
